    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review and extend Sunday Trading Hours",
        "additional_details": "We think extending Sunday trading hours would:\r\n\u2022 Create more jobs and income opportunities for workers.\r\n\u2022 Boost the economy by increasing business revenue and tax contributions.\r\n\u2022 Provide consumers with greater flexibility and convenience.\r\n \r\nOther countries have modernized their trading laws successfully. We think it\u2019s time for the UK to follow suit and support businesses, workers, and shoppers alike.",
        "background": "We call on Parliament to review and amend Sunday trading laws to allow shops to open for longer. We think current restrictions are outdated and do not reflect modern lifestyles or economic needs.",
